    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Saturday about a letter urging the National Association of Evangelicals to force its vice president for government affairs to stop speaking out on global warming included incorrect information from the letter about two of the signers. Gary L. Bauer is chairman of American Values, not president of Coalitions for America. Paul Weyrich is national chairman of Coalitions for America, not chairman of American Values.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
